  <description>
    <p>
      PeaZip is free file archiver utility, based on Open Source technologies of 
      7-Zip, p7zip, Brotli, FreeArc, PAQ, Zstandard, and PEA projects.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cross-platform, full-featured but user-friendly alternative to WinRar, WinZip 
      and similar general purpose archive manager applications, open and extract 
      200+ archive formats: 001, 7Z, ACE, ARC, ARJ, BR, BZ2, CAB, DMG, GZ, ISO, LHA, 
      PAQ, PEA, RAR, TAR, UDF, WIM, XZ, ZIP, ZIPX, ZST - view full list of supported 
      archive file formats for archiving and for extraction.
    </p>
  </description>
  
